title: Comptel Corporation Q3 2015 Quarterly Report Announcement on 20 October 2015 at 8 am EET
text:
Comptel Corporation Q3 2015 Quarterly Report Announcement on 20 October 2015 at 8 am EET ET | Source: Comptel multilang-release 
Comptel Corporation’s Q3 2015 Quarterly Report will be published on Tuesday 20 October 2015 at 8 am EET. 

Investor meeting in Finnish will be hel d as follows: 
Time: Tuesday 20 October at 10.00 – 11.00 am EET 
Place : GLO Hotel Kluuvi, Kluuvikatu 4, 00100 HELSINKI 

International investors can schedule a call with CEO Juhani Hintikka and/or CFO Tom Jansson by sending a meeting request to IR Communications, communications@comptel.com , by Friday 16 October.
